txt.en: You have defeated a number of goblins from Nan Wathren, and reclaimed the relics of ancient Meluinen. You have honoured the memory of the Elves who once roamed these lands.

Relics of Meluinen can be found on goblins and in caches in central Nan Wathren, in the southern North Downs.

You should collect the stolen relics of Meluinen, so that they may someday be returned.

<rgb=#FF0000>Small Fellowship Recommended.</rgb>

Goblins of Nan Wathren have been found to be in possession of valuable Elvish relics pillaged from the refuge of Meluinen.

Goblins of Nan Wathren have been found to be in possession of valuable Elvish relics pillaged from an unknown place called Meluinen.

You should gather relics from the goblins and their hidden caches, in hope that they may someday be restored to Meluinen.

<rgb=#FF0000>Small Fellowship Recommended.</rgb>
